WEBVTT

00:04.004 --> 00:05.806
* SHE SAYS SHE WANTS TO DANCE
'CAUSE SHE LIKES TO GROOVE *

00:05.873 --> 00:07.741
* COME ON, FATSO,
AND JUST BUST A MOVE *

00:07.808 --> 00:09.510
* OH, YEAH *

00:09.577 --> 00:10.978
* OH, YEAH *

00:11.045 --> 00:12.813
* OH, YEAH *

00:12.880 --> 00:14.515
* OH, YEAH *

00:14.582 --> 00:15.783
* OH, YEAH *

00:15.849 --> 00:16.917
HIT ME!

00:16.984 --> 00:18.086
* OH, YEAH *

00:18.152 --> 00:20.054
* OH, YEAH *

00:20.121 --> 00:21.722
* OH, YEAH *

00:23.857 --> 00:25.959
CARL?

00:26.026 --> 00:27.461
CARL!

00:31.132 --> 00:33.734
OH, BIG GUY!

00:50.718 --> 00:51.552
[HONK!]

00:51.619 --> 00:54.021
HOLD ON! WHAT'S THAT?
WHAT? WHAT?

00:54.088 --> 00:56.157
OH...OH!

01:00.594 --> 01:01.829
OH, GOOD. YOU'RE UP.

01:03.197 --> 01:04.998
COULDN'T YOU SEE
THAT I WAS SLEEP?

01:05.065 --> 01:06.667
OH, ABSOLUTELY.

01:12.273 --> 01:13.341
GO HOME, STEVE.

01:13.407 --> 01:15.276
BUT I REALLY NEED A FAVOR.

01:15.343 --> 01:18.078
FORGET IT. THIS IS MY
DAY OFF AND I'M GONNA RELAX.

01:18.146 --> 01:21.048
I AM NOT MOVING
FROM THIS SPOT.
I AM A TREE.

01:21.115 --> 01:22.250
BUT..

01:22.316 --> 01:24.585
THAT'S ENOUGH.
CARL WINSLOW HAS SPOKEN.

01:27.888 --> 01:29.823
WELL, OKAY.

01:29.890 --> 01:32.860
IT'S JUST THAT MY PARENTS AND I
WERE SUPPOSED TO GO TO HAWAII,

01:32.926 --> 01:36.764
BUT SOMEHOW THEY LEFT
FOR THE AIRPORT
WITHOUT ME.

01:38.266 --> 01:39.833
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD
GIVE ME A LIFT,

01:39.900 --> 01:43.837
BUT I'LL JUST SPEND
MY NEXT TWO WEEKS WITH YOU.

01:45.072 --> 01:46.440
COME ON, LET'S GO!

01:46.507 --> 01:48.176
WHOA!

01:48.242 --> 01:49.343
I'LL GET YOU
ON THAT PLANE

01:49.410 --> 01:51.845
IF I HAVE TO CHASE IT
DOWN THE RUNWAY!

02:03.457 --> 02:05.793
* IT'S A RARE CONDITION *

02:05.859 --> 02:07.261
* IN THIS DAY AND AGE *

02:07.328 --> 02:10.731
* TO READ ANY GOOD NEWS
ON THE NEWSPAPER PAGE *

02:10.798 --> 02:14.134
* AND LOVE AND TRADITION
OF THE GRAND DESIGN *

02:14.202 --> 02:18.539
* SOME PEOPLE SAY
IS EVEN HARDER TO FIND *

02:18.606 --> 02:21.642
* WELL, THEN, THERE MUST BE
SOME MAGIC CLUE *

02:21.709 --> 02:25.846
* INSIDE THESE GENTLE WALLS *

02:25.913 --> 02:29.550
* 'CAUSE ALL I SEE
IS A TOWER OF DREAMS *

02:29.617 --> 02:33.621
* REAL LOVE BURSTIN'
OUT OF EVERY SEAM *

02:34.822 --> 02:37.358
* AS DAYS GO BY *

02:37.425 --> 02:41.529
* WE'RE GONNA FILL
OUR HOUSE WITH HAPPINESS *

02:41.595 --> 02:44.598
* THE MOON MAY CRY *

02:44.665 --> 02:48.436
* WE'RE GONNA SMOTHER
THE BLUES WITH TENDERNESS *

02:48.502 --> 02:51.739
* AS DAYS GO BY *

02:51.805 --> 02:55.209
* THERE'S ROOM FOR YOU
ROOM FOR ME *

02:55.276 --> 02:59.179
* FOR GENTLE HEARTS
AN OPPORTUNITY *

02:59.247 --> 03:02.550
* AS DAYS GO BY *

03:02.616 --> 03:06.854
* IT'S THE BIGGER LOVE
OF THE FAMILY *

03:18.399 --> 03:19.166
HI, HONEY.

03:19.233 --> 03:20.668
HI.

03:20.734 --> 03:22.570
HARRIETTE, I'D LIKE YOU
TO MEET MIKE FORBES,

03:22.636 --> 03:25.273
FRESH OUT OF THE ACADEMY
AND ASSIGNED TO ME.

03:25.339 --> 03:27.107
HI. IT'S A PLEASURE
TO MEET YOU,

03:27.174 --> 03:28.576
AND I'M HONORED
TO BE PARTNERED

03:28.642 --> 03:32.313
WITH CARL
"MAKE MY DAY" WINSLOW.

03:34.948 --> 03:38.486
CARL "MAKE MY DAY"
WINSLOW?

03:38.552 --> 03:39.553
YEAH.

03:39.620 --> 03:42.222
YOU KNOW,
MY NICKNAME

03:42.290 --> 03:44.492
THAT EVERYONE
CALLS ME.

03:44.558 --> 03:46.494
OH, OH, OH.
SURE, SURE!

03:46.560 --> 03:47.995
I GUESS THEY CHANGED IT

03:48.061 --> 03:50.664
FROM CARL
"MAKE IT TO GO" WINSLOW.

03:57.571 --> 03:59.607
SHE'S A TERRIFIC
LADY.

03:59.673 --> 04:00.708
AH, THE BEST.

04:00.774 --> 04:02.543
SAY, MIKE,
YOU SAID THAT
YOU WANTED TO SEE

04:02.610 --> 04:04.211
A DEPARTMENTAL
COMMENDATION.

04:04.278 --> 04:05.713
YEAH. YOU GOT ONE?

04:05.779 --> 04:08.081
WELL, ACTUALLY...

04:08.148 --> 04:09.950
THREE.

04:10.017 --> 04:12.152
WOW, SARGE,
YOU'RE A HERO.

04:12.219 --> 04:14.822
WELL, I WOULDN'T...

04:14.888 --> 04:16.790
YEAH.

04:16.857 --> 04:18.492
GRAB A SEAT, MIKE.

04:21.261 --> 04:22.896
OH, GIRL, I LOVE
MY NEW OUTFIT!

04:22.963 --> 04:24.565
BUT YOU SHOULD HAVE
GOT THE SHOES.

04:24.632 --> 04:26.166
THEY WERE TOO EXPENSIVE.

04:26.233 --> 04:29.570
DO WHAT I DO,
WEAR 'EM A WEEK
AND TAKE 'EM BACK.

04:29.637 --> 04:31.739
UH-UH!
YOU'RE A TRIP.

04:31.805 --> 04:32.740
NO, I'M NOT.

04:32.806 --> 04:35.576
I COULD NEVER
DO A THING LIKE--

04:40.914 --> 04:42.015
HI.

04:42.082 --> 04:43.951
HI.

04:45.353 --> 04:46.920
SAY HI.

04:47.321 --> 04:48.756
HI.

04:50.858 --> 04:53.293
NOT TO ME. TO HIM.

04:56.129 --> 04:57.765
HI.

04:59.967 --> 05:00.801
I'M MIKE FORBES.

05:00.868 --> 05:04.572
IS ONE OF YOU
LOVELY LADIES LAURA?

05:04.638 --> 05:06.106
I AM.

05:06.173 --> 05:10.143
GREAT, I'M YOUR DAD'S
NEW PARTNER.
NICE TO MEET YOU.

05:10.210 --> 05:12.380
NICE TO MEET YOU, TOO...

05:12.446 --> 05:14.648
AND SHAKE.

05:16.450 --> 05:18.819
I MEAN HANDS.

05:21.422 --> 05:23.824
HEY MIKE, ON FRIDAY
HARRIETTE'S GOING TO MAKE US

05:23.891 --> 05:26.860
A BIG TURKEY DINNER
WITH ALL THE TRIMMINGS.

05:32.500 --> 05:34.468
YOU LIKE BURGERS?

05:34.535 --> 05:36.336
SOUNDS GREAT,
SARGE.

05:36.404 --> 05:38.372
OH, I SEE YOU MET
MY LITTLE PRINCESS HERE.

05:38.439 --> 05:40.541
YEAH, I SURE DID.

05:40.608 --> 05:43.977
DAD, I'M NOT LITTLE.

05:44.044 --> 05:46.279
LAURA, I HOPE
YOU DIDN'T BLOW
YOUR WHOLE ALLOWANCE

05:46.346 --> 05:48.048
AT THE RECORD
STORE.

05:49.617 --> 05:51.419
DAD, IT'S MY MONEY!

05:51.485 --> 05:53.454
YOU KNOW,
I HAVE A JOB.

05:55.222 --> 05:57.391
COME ON, MIKE.
HARRIETTE'S GOT
MY COMMENDATIONS

05:57.458 --> 05:59.893
HUNG OVER
THE WATER HEATER.

06:00.861 --> 06:02.062
BYE.

06:04.765 --> 06:05.933
WOOF!

06:07.334 --> 06:08.268
HIT ME, MAX.

06:08.335 --> 06:09.437
WHY?

06:09.503 --> 06:12.406
I WALK IN AND SEE THE BABE
ON MY COUCH,

06:12.473 --> 06:13.974
AND WHAT DO I DO?

06:14.041 --> 06:15.676
ACT LIKE A GEEK?

06:16.510 --> 06:19.346
I WENT WAY BEYOND GEEK.

06:19.413 --> 06:22.015
I WENT INTO GEEK WARP.

06:22.082 --> 06:24.217
YOU'RE BEING
TOO HARD ON YOURSELF.

06:24.284 --> 06:26.119
LOOK ON THE BRIGHT SIDE.

06:26.186 --> 06:27.354
WHICH IS?

06:27.421 --> 06:29.590
IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW FOOLISH YOU LOOKED,

06:29.657 --> 06:31.859
SINCE MIKE DOESN'T KNOW
YOU'RE ALIVE.

06:44.404 --> 06:48.175
* ALOHA EY,
ALOHA OY *

06:48.241 --> 06:51.111
* ALOHA...OOH *

06:53.647 --> 06:55.783
EXCUSE ME,
WOULD ONE OF YOU LOVELY LADIES

06:55.849 --> 06:59.119
LIKE TO SLAP A LITTLE
SPF-40 ON MY LOWER LUMBAR?

07:06.393 --> 07:07.495
WELL!

07:07.561 --> 07:09.763
THERE GOES
HOITY AND TOITY.

07:12.833 --> 07:15.035
THIS LOOKS LIKE
A NICE SPOT...

07:15.102 --> 07:19.573
DON'T YOU THINK,
MY LITTLE BEACH BUNNY?

07:21.008 --> 07:23.644
[HUMMING]

07:28.048 --> 07:31.151
[POLKA PLAYS]

07:39.593 --> 07:41.629
[TURNS RADIO OFF]

07:41.695 --> 07:44.164
WHOO! AH! HOT, HOT!

07:48.569 --> 07:50.370
LET'S SEE...

07:50.437 --> 07:53.574
CHICAGO IS THAT WAY...

07:55.175 --> 07:59.079
AND...TELSTAR...

07:59.146 --> 08:01.849
IS THATAWAY!

08:05.653 --> 08:07.287
* HAWAII IS THE PLACE TO BE *

08:07.354 --> 08:08.856
* DOO DAH, DOO DAH *

08:08.922 --> 08:10.691
* ON THE BEACH ON WAIKIKI *

08:10.758 --> 08:12.159
* ALL THE DOO DAH DAY *

08:12.225 --> 08:13.761
* GONNA SEE DON HO *

08:13.827 --> 08:15.763
* WOULDN'T MISS HIS SHOW... *

08:15.829 --> 08:17.497
[RING]

08:18.699 --> 08:21.034
NO, GIVE ME
THE PHONE!

08:21.101 --> 08:23.236
GIVE--GIVE!

08:26.273 --> 08:28.175
UH...UH!

08:28.241 --> 08:30.911
TALK TO ME, BABE.

08:32.312 --> 08:35.015
ALOHA, EDDO.
IT'S ME--STEVE.

08:39.119 --> 08:41.321
HELLO...HELLO?

08:41.388 --> 08:43.090
HELLO?

08:44.191 --> 08:45.525
HELLO!

08:47.260 --> 08:50.564
UH... NO HABLO TELEFONO.

08:51.865 --> 08:54.001
QUIT KIDDING AROUND,
ICKIWAKA.

08:54.067 --> 08:58.505
TELL MY LITTLE LA LA
IT'S HER MAIN MAN, KEPANO.

08:58.572 --> 08:59.840
HUH?

08:59.907 --> 09:02.442
THAT'S ALL OF OUR NAMES
IN HAWAIIAN.

09:02.509 --> 09:05.312
OH, NEAT. BYE.

09:05.378 --> 09:06.647
NO, NO, NO. NO.

09:06.714 --> 09:09.382
I REALLY NEED
TO TALK TO LAURA.

09:09.449 --> 09:12.085
YOU REALLY NEED
TO TALK TO LAURA?

09:12.152 --> 09:13.587
NO. NO.

09:13.654 --> 09:16.790
OKAY. HERE SHE IS.

09:19.660 --> 09:21.629
WHAT DO YOU WANT,
STEVE?

09:21.695 --> 09:25.065
SO, MY LITTLE
MACADAMIA NUT.

09:25.132 --> 09:26.466
DO YOU MISS ME?

09:26.533 --> 09:28.401
[KISS KISS]

09:28.468 --> 09:30.704
LIKE I MISS
A ROOT CANAL.

09:30.771 --> 09:34.642
GOOD NEWS,
I'VE BEEN FAITHFUL TO YOU.

09:34.708 --> 09:37.544
THAT'S REALLY NOT
NECESSARY, STEVE.

09:37.611 --> 09:39.212
BUT I RESISTED
EVERY TEMPTATION.

09:39.279 --> 09:42.916
I'M BEING PURSUED
BY A BIG BUXOM ISLANDER, KALIKI.

09:42.983 --> 09:45.786
THAT'S HAWAIIAN
FOR "WOMAN WHO BLOCKS THE SUN."

09:47.688 --> 09:49.990
STEVE, I HEAR
A LOT OF STATIC.

09:50.057 --> 09:51.224
WHAT?

09:51.291 --> 09:53.894
LAURA? LAURA!

09:53.961 --> 09:55.829
OH, MY LAURA.
GOT TO GET HER! GOT TO GET HER.

09:55.896 --> 09:59.066
I'VE GOT TO GET HER BACK!
GOT TO GET HER BACK.

10:08.541 --> 10:10.077
HI, KALIKI.

10:11.244 --> 10:13.647
LOVE THAT MUUMUU.

10:19.286 --> 10:21.188
* WORK THAT BODY,
WORK THAT BODY *

10:21.254 --> 10:24.658
* MAKE SURE YOU DON'T
HURT NOBODY *

10:24.725 --> 10:26.794
HURRY UP, SLOWPOKE!

10:28.561 --> 10:30.363
GIVE ME A BREAK.

10:34.668 --> 10:36.069
I WOULDN'T
HAVE MADE IT

10:36.136 --> 10:38.371
IF THAT DOG
HADN'T CHASED ME.

10:40.640 --> 10:42.910
HI, MOM.
JOGGING AGAIN?

10:42.976 --> 10:45.145
LISTEN MOM,
CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A MINUTE?

10:45.212 --> 10:48.115
SURE, HONEY.
JUST GIVE ME SOME TIME

10:48.181 --> 10:49.683
TO CATCH MY BREATH.

10:49.750 --> 10:51.819
OKAY. READY YET?

10:54.722 --> 10:56.857
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND,
HONEY?

10:56.924 --> 10:59.092
MOTHER, THERE'S THIS GUY
I SORT OF LIKE,

10:59.159 --> 11:01.128
BUT HE DOESN'T EVEN KNOW
I'M ALIVE.

11:01.194 --> 11:03.363
HOW DO I GET HIM
TO NOTICE ME?

11:03.430 --> 11:05.699
JUST BE YOURSELF.

11:05.766 --> 11:07.467
GIVE HIM A CHANCE
TO GET TO KNOW YOU.

11:07.534 --> 11:10.070
HE'LL COME AROUND.

11:10.137 --> 11:11.404
THAT'S ALL?

11:11.471 --> 11:12.672
THAT'S ALL.

11:12.740 --> 11:14.842
[SHUDDERS]

11:16.509 --> 11:18.045
[SHUDDERS]

11:19.312 --> 11:20.647
WHAT?

11:20.714 --> 11:23.016
NOTHING.
SHE'S YOUR DAUGHTER.

11:23.083 --> 11:25.853
I SUPPOSE
YOU HAVE
BETTER ADVICE?

11:25.919 --> 11:28.288
WATCH ME WORK, HONEY.

11:28.355 --> 11:30.190
LAURA...

11:30.257 --> 11:32.860
MEN ARE LIKE FISH.

11:32.926 --> 11:34.561
IF YOU WANT
TO CATCH ONE,

11:34.627 --> 11:37.798
PUT SOME BAIT
ON YOUR HOOK.

11:37.865 --> 11:39.532
HOW DO I DO THAT?

11:39.599 --> 11:42.469
SEXY PERFUME,
SOFT HAIR,

11:42.535 --> 11:44.571
AND A KILLER OUTFIT.

11:44.637 --> 11:47.775
GIRL, WHEN YOU
WALK AWAY,

11:47.841 --> 11:50.878
DRAG HIS HEART
BEHIND YOU.

11:52.245 --> 11:53.981
HEEL!

11:55.548 --> 11:56.817
OH, WOW!

11:56.884 --> 11:59.019
OH, PLEASE.

12:08.661 --> 12:10.831
COME ON IN, MIKE.

12:10.898 --> 12:12.833
AND BASK IN THE KNOWLEDGE

12:12.900 --> 12:15.468
THAT A COUPLE OF BEAT COPS
HAVE MADE THE MEAN STREETS

12:15.535 --> 12:20.173
OF CHI-TOWN TOWN A LITTLE SAFER
FOR JOHN Q PUBLIC.

12:22.976 --> 12:25.745
GEE, I WISH I COULD
TALK LIKE THAT.

12:28.048 --> 12:30.750
YOU WILL SON.
SOME DAY.

12:31.819 --> 12:33.921
HEY, YOU'RE ALREADY OFF
TO A GOOD START.

12:33.987 --> 12:35.555
YOU MADE YOUR
FIRST COLLAR TODAY.

12:35.622 --> 12:36.924
I SURE DID, SARGE.

12:36.990 --> 12:39.159
AND THANKS
FOR LETTING ME DO
ALL THE PAPERWORK.

12:39.226 --> 12:41.361
HEY, HOW ELSE
YOU GONNA LEARN?

12:41.428 --> 12:42.796
HEY, TAKE A SEAT.

12:42.863 --> 12:44.097
I'LL SEE WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH DINNER.

12:44.164 --> 12:45.532
OKAY.

13:03.050 --> 13:05.118
[BREATHY VOICE]
HELLO, MICHAEL.

13:29.910 --> 13:30.911
MICHAEL...

13:30.978 --> 13:33.981
IT'S SO NICE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

13:34.047 --> 13:36.950
ET QUELLE SURPRISE.

13:40.287 --> 13:41.654
IT'S NICE
TO SEE YOU TOO

13:41.721 --> 13:44.491
BUT DID YOU FORGET
I WAS COMING OVER
FOR DINNER?

13:44.557 --> 13:46.459
I MUST HAVE.

13:46.526 --> 13:49.129
SILLY ME.

13:49.196 --> 13:51.331
IF I HAD REMEMBERED,
I WOULD HAVE...

13:51.398 --> 13:53.100
DRESSED.

13:57.270 --> 13:59.572
THAT'S, UH,
QUITE A PERFUME
YOU'RE WEARING.

13:59.639 --> 14:02.175
IT'S VERY...

14:02.242 --> 14:04.477
NOTICEABLE.

14:04.544 --> 14:06.313
IT'S CALLED...

14:06.379 --> 14:08.248
UNLEASHED.

14:09.816 --> 14:11.518
AH.

14:11.584 --> 14:13.653
SHALL WE...

14:13.720 --> 14:15.388
AS THEY SAY IN EUROPE,

14:15.455 --> 14:17.958
SIT?

14:19.492 --> 14:21.328
OKAY.

14:28.035 --> 14:30.437
SO, HOW WAS YOUR DAY?

14:30.503 --> 14:32.906
GREAT. YOUR DAD AND I
CAUGHT A BURGLAR.

14:32.973 --> 14:35.976
OH, MY!
YOU WERE IN DANGER!

14:36.043 --> 14:38.211
NOT REALLY, YOUR DAD DID
ALL THE DANGEROUS STUFF.

14:38.278 --> 14:40.580
I JUST FILLED OUT
THE REPORTS.

14:40.647 --> 14:42.049
STILL...

14:42.115 --> 14:44.484
YOU TOOK A RISK.

14:44.551 --> 14:46.386
OF WHAT,
A PAPER CUT?

14:50.323 --> 14:52.993
HA HA HA HA!

15:01.801 --> 15:04.204
OH, GOSH!

15:05.538 --> 15:07.474
YOU TICKLE ME.

15:11.678 --> 15:13.713
YOU KNOW...

15:13.780 --> 15:16.950
I FIND HUMOR VERY...

15:17.017 --> 15:19.519
ATTRACTIVE...

15:19.586 --> 15:21.221
IN A MAN.

15:21.921 --> 15:23.823
WE'VE GOT DRINKS.

15:23.890 --> 15:26.693
AND WE'VE GOT
HORS D'OEUVRES.

15:37.670 --> 15:39.639
HELLO, MOTHER.

15:41.574 --> 15:42.542
AUNTIE.

15:44.411 --> 15:46.346
HELLO...

15:46.413 --> 15:49.349
LAURA?

15:49.416 --> 15:50.483
UH--UH, MIKE,

15:50.550 --> 15:52.919
THIS IS MY SISTER
RACHEL CRAWFORD.

15:52.986 --> 15:55.355
HI, HOW ARE YOU?
IT'S NICE TO MEET YOU.

15:58.225 --> 16:00.760
HARRIETTE,
I THINK I HEAR
THE OVEN TIMER.

16:00.827 --> 16:02.429
WE DON'T
HAVE AN OVEN TIMER.

16:02.495 --> 16:05.865
OH, YOU MEAN
THE NEW SILENT
OVEN TIMER.

16:05.932 --> 16:07.867
OKAY.
EXCUSE US.

16:07.934 --> 16:10.237
WHO MAKES
SILENT OVEN TIMERS?

16:10.303 --> 16:12.739
THE SAME PEOPLE
WHO MAKE SILENT ALARMS.

16:15.475 --> 16:16.409
GOOD NEWS!

16:16.476 --> 16:18.678
I'VE FOUND
MORE COMMENDATIONS.

16:18.745 --> 16:20.147
LAURA?

16:21.914 --> 16:23.816
YES, FATHER?

16:23.883 --> 16:25.818
WHAT'S WITH THIS GETUP?

16:25.885 --> 16:27.087
UH, CARL--

16:27.154 --> 16:29.989
IS THIS FOR THE SCHOOL PLAY?

16:30.057 --> 16:30.890
NO, IT ISN'T.

16:30.957 --> 16:32.192
WELL, THEN...

16:32.259 --> 16:34.494
WHY ARE YOU WEARING
ALL THAT MAKE-UP?

16:37.630 --> 16:39.299
EXCUSE ME.

16:46.439 --> 16:49.142
WELL, WHAT'S THE MATTER?
WHAT DID I DO?

16:50.177 --> 16:52.645
UH, COULD YOU
EXCUSE US, PLEASE?

16:52.712 --> 16:53.680
SURE.

16:53.746 --> 16:54.747
WHAT? OW!

16:54.814 --> 16:56.516
WHAT?

16:56.583 --> 16:58.085
[RING]

16:58.151 --> 16:59.886
EXCUSE ME.

16:59.952 --> 17:00.887
HELLO.

17:00.953 --> 17:02.689
HELLO, RACHEL?

17:02.755 --> 17:03.956
STEVE?

17:04.023 --> 17:05.525
YEAH, I NEED
A BIG FAVOR.

17:05.592 --> 17:06.759
PRONTO.

17:06.826 --> 17:09.529
YOU SEE, IT SEEMS
THAT I'VE SPURNED
THE ADVANCES

17:09.596 --> 17:13.133
OF A WOMAN NAMED KALIKI
ONE TIME TOO MANY.

17:13.200 --> 17:17.637
SHE'S DRIVEN ME
INTO THE SAND
LIKE A TENT SPIKE.

17:17.704 --> 17:20.373
STEVE, WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO DO ABOUT IT FROM HERE?

17:20.440 --> 17:22.008
COULD YOU CALL
THE CONCIERGE

17:22.075 --> 17:24.211
AND ASK THEM COME
AND DIG ME OUT?

17:24.277 --> 17:26.012
I TRIED
CALLING HIM MYSELF,

17:26.079 --> 17:27.914
BUT HE RECOGNIZED
MY VOICE.

17:27.980 --> 17:29.816
COULD YOU CALL
FAIRLY SOON?

17:29.882 --> 17:32.252
THE TIDE'S COMING IN.

17:35.122 --> 17:36.889
OOH! OOH!
AND HURRY!

17:36.956 --> 17:38.458
HURRY!

17:57.110 --> 17:59.212
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

17:59.279 --> 18:01.848
LAURA? IT'S ME.

18:01.914 --> 18:03.250
CAN I COME IN?

18:03.316 --> 18:05.518
IT'S YOUR HOUSE.

18:12.792 --> 18:15.094
[SIGHS]

18:32.345 --> 18:36.583
I GUESS I REALLY
DID IT THIS TIME, HUH?

18:36.649 --> 18:38.685
I KNOW I'VE PUT MY FOOT
IN MY MOUTH BEFORE

18:38.751 --> 18:40.153
BUT I THINK THIS TIME

18:40.220 --> 18:42.355
I WAS TASTING
MY KNEE JOINT.

18:44.056 --> 18:47.260
COME ON, HONEY, HELP ME OUT
A LITTLE. TALK TO ME.

18:51.063 --> 18:53.366
DAD,
YOU HUMILIATED ME.

18:53.433 --> 18:56.203
MIKE THINKS
I'M A TOTAL FOOL.

18:56.269 --> 18:58.905
HONEY, I ADMIT
I WAS OUT OF LINE,

18:58.971 --> 19:00.307
BUT, HEY...

19:00.373 --> 19:02.175
JUST THINK, ONE DAY WE'LL
LOOK BACK AT THIS

19:02.242 --> 19:05.044
AND LAUGH.

19:05.111 --> 19:06.879
IT WON'T BE SOON.

19:12.219 --> 19:13.420
I'VE BEEN SO BUSY

19:13.486 --> 19:16.589
TRYING
TO PLAY SUPERCOP
FOR MIKE, THAT...

19:16.656 --> 19:18.925
HONEY, I DIDN'T EVEN NOTICE
YOU HAD A CRUSH ON HIM.

19:18.991 --> 19:20.293
IT'S NOT A CRUSH.

19:20.360 --> 19:23.930
IT'S A NATURAL EXTENSION
OF MY ESSENTIAL WOMANHOOD.

19:23.996 --> 19:27.500
I MEAN, DAD, IT'S NOT LIKE
I WAS GOING TO MARRY THE GUY.

19:27.567 --> 19:29.936
GOOD,
BECAUSE HE'S ENGAGED.

19:31.204 --> 19:33.005
OUCH.

19:33.072 --> 19:35.375
NOW I FEEL EVEN WORSE.

19:39.879 --> 19:41.814
HEY...

19:43.416 --> 19:46.018
YOU REMEMBER
HUMPHREY BEARGART?

19:46.085 --> 19:47.387
SURE.

19:47.454 --> 19:48.621
YOU WON HIM FOR ME

19:48.688 --> 19:51.491
AT THE COUNTY FAIR
ON MY 6th BIRTHDAY.

19:51.558 --> 19:54.461
I REMEMBER YOU TRIED
TO TALK LIKE HIM.

19:56.529 --> 19:59.098
[IMITATING BOGART]
OF ALL THE COUNTY FAIRS
IN THE WORLD,

19:59.165 --> 20:01.368
SHE HAD
TO WALK INTO MINE.

20:03.270 --> 20:05.705
KEEP WORKING ON IT.

20:07.707 --> 20:10.810
YOU KNOW, I REMEMBER TO WIN
HUMPHREY HERE,

20:10.877 --> 20:13.246
I HAD TO SHOOT WATER
INTO A CLOWN'S MOUTH

20:13.313 --> 20:15.214
AT 10 CENTS A TRY.

20:15.282 --> 20:17.850
38 BUCKS LATER,
WE HAD HIM.

20:22.255 --> 20:24.924
YOU KNOW, LAURA,
IN THOSE DAYS,

20:24.991 --> 20:26.626
YOU WERE
DADDY'S LITTLE GIRL.

20:28.395 --> 20:29.962
MAN, IF I COULD HAVE
FROZEN TIME,

20:30.029 --> 20:33.966
I THINK I'D HAVE KEPT YOU
6 YEARS OLD FOREVER.

20:34.033 --> 20:36.269
BUT I COULDN'T,

20:36.336 --> 20:37.570
AND NOW YOU'VE GROWN

20:37.637 --> 20:41.140
INTO A BEAUTIFUL
YOUNG LADY,

20:41.207 --> 20:42.575
AND, SWEETHEART,

20:42.642 --> 20:45.845
I PROMISE TO TRY
TO TREAT YOU LIKE
ONE FROM NOW ON.

20:54.086 --> 20:56.656
[SIGHS]

20:58.658 --> 21:00.593
DADDY?

21:00.660 --> 21:01.861
YEAH?

21:01.928 --> 21:04.764
[IMITATING BOGART]
WE'LL ALWAYS HAVE
THE COUNTY FAIR.

21:32.291 --> 21:34.961
ALOHA,
WIKI WINSLOWS!

21:35.027 --> 21:36.128
STEVE,

21:36.195 --> 21:37.597
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

21:37.664 --> 21:39.599
WELL, MY FLIGHT
JUST GOT IN
FROM HAWAII,

21:39.666 --> 21:41.000
AND
I COULDN'T WAIT

21:41.067 --> 21:43.069
TO GIVE YOU
YOUR SOUVENIRS.

21:43.135 --> 21:47.039
STEVE,
IT'S 1:32 IN THE MORNING.

21:47.106 --> 21:50.076
OH...IT'S NEVER
TOO LATE FOR...

21:50.142 --> 21:52.178
HAND-CARVED
COCONUTS.

21:52.244 --> 21:54.180
HEE HEE HEE.
[SNORTS]

21:54.246 --> 21:56.282
* ALOHA EY *

21:56.349 --> 21:58.250
* ALOHA OY *

21:58.317 --> 22:00.720
* ALOHA OOH-OOH *
